
---

# 🧹 **.gitignore (Safe for GitHub, Protects Secrets & Build Files)**

```gitignore
# Build output
bin/
obj/
out/

# User-specific files
*.user
*.suo
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates

# Logs
*.log

# Secrets (VERY IMPORTANT)
secrets.json
appsettings.Development.json

# Database files
*.mdf
*.ldf
*.bak
*.db

# VSCode
.vscode/

# Rider / JetBrains
.idea/

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Publish output
publish/
